column2: SELECT TOP #  s.apogee_id,s.ra, s.dec, s.glon, s.glat,  s.vhelio_avg,s.vscatter,  a.teff, a.teff_err, a.logg, a.logg_err, a.fe_h, a.fe_h_err  dbo.fApogeeAspcapFlagN(a.aspcapflag),  dbo.fApogeeStarFlagN(s.starflag) FROM apogeeStar s  JOIN aspcapStar a on a.apstar_id = s.apstar_id WHERE (a.aspcapflag & dbo.fApogeeAspcapFlag(&&&)) = #)
